{"parse":{"title":"Full Mechanics","pageid":119035,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><figure class=\"thumb  show-info-icon\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\" style=\"width: 150px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/b7/FullMechanicsLogo.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20210202025004\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Full Mechanics Logo\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"35\" class=\"thumbimage lazyload\" data-image-name=\"FullMechanicsLogo.jpg\" data-image-key=\"FullMechanicsLogo.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/b7/FullMechanicsLogo.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20210202025004\" /></a> \t<noscript><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/b7/FullMechanicsLogo.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20210202025004\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Full Mechanics Logo\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/b7/FullMechanicsLogo.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20210202025004\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"35\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"FullMechanicsLogo.jpg\" data-image-key=\"FullMechanicsLogo.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/b7/FullMechanicsLogo.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20210202025004\" /></a></noscript> \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:FullMechanicsLogo.jpg\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">Full Mechanics Logo</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p><b>Full Mechanics (FM)</b> is a line of <a href=\"/wiki/Gunpla\" title=\"Gunpla\">Gunpla</a> established in 2021, designed to feature certain mobile suits in 1/100 scale but separate from the&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Master_Grade\" title=\"Master Grade\">Master Grade</a> (MG)&#160;line. In contrast with the <a href=\"/wiki/Reborn-One_Hundred\" title=\"Reborn-One Hundred\">Reborn-One Hundred</a> (RE/100) line, this line features mobile suits from timelines outside of <a href=\"/wiki/Universal_Century\" title=\"Universal Century\">Universal Century</a> only. Aside from the <i>Gundam</i> franchise, the Full Mechanics line has hosted other mecha anime series such as <i>Amaim Warrior at the Borderline</i>.\n</p><p>This line should not be confused with the <a href=\"/wiki/1/100_IRON-BLOODED_ORPHANS\" title=\"1/100 IRON-BLOODED ORPHANS\">1/100 IRON-BLOODED ORPHANS Full Mechanics</a> line from 2016, which is likely its predecessor.\n</p><p>This article covers only the Gundam releases.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Lineup\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Lineup</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Notes_&amp;_Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes &amp; Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lineup\">Lineup</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FFull_Mechanics%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Regular\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Regular</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Exclusives\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Exclusives</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>FM #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th>\n<th>Link\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>001 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/d/d6/FM_Calamity_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20210625104939\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"FM Calamity Gundam\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/d/d6/FM_Calamity_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20210625104939\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"202\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"FM Calamity Gundam.jpg\" data-image-key=\"FM_Calamity_Gundam.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X131_Calamity_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X131 Calamity Gundam\">GAT-X131 Calamity Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,000\n</td>\n<td>2021 June\n</td>\n<td>First Full Mechanics released, and the first release from the <a href=\"/wiki/Cosmic_Era\" title=\"Cosmic Era\">Cosmic Era</a> timeline.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1095\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>002 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/8c/FM_Raider_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20220517133920\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"FM Raider Gundam\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/8c/FM_Raider_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20220517133920\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"164\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"FM Raider Gundam.jpg\" data-image-key=\"FM_Raider_Gundam.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X370_Raider_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X370 Raider Gundam\">GAT-X370 Raider Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,000\n</td>\n<td>2022 May\n</td>\n<td>First transformable/separable kit in the series. Includes clear support stand for Mjolnir Spherical Breaker.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1094\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>003 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/69/FM_Gundam_Aerial.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20230311214454\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"FM Gundam Aerial\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/69/FM_Gundam_Aerial.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20230311214454\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"202\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"FM Gundam Aerial.jpg\" data-image-key=\"FM_Gundam_Aerial.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/XVX-016_Gundam_Aerial\" title=\"XVX-016 Gundam Aerial\">XVX-016 Gundam Aerial</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_the_Witch_from_Mercury\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam the Witch from Mercury\">Mobile Suit Gundam the Witch from Mercury</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a53,800\n</td>\n<td>2023 April\n</td>\n<td>First release from the <a href=\"/wiki/Ad_Stella\" title=\"Ad Stella\">Ad Stella</a> timeline. Features red chrome plated Shell Unit parts. Escutcheon shield transforms into a kit-exclusive claw mode. Originally planned to be released in 2023 March, but was delayed due to unspecified reason<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>1<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1093\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>004 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/98/FM_Forbidden_Gundam.jpeg/revision/latest?cb=20230807133634\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"FM Forbidden Gundam\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"164\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"FM Forbidden Gundam.jpeg\" data-image-key=\"FM_Forbidden_Gundam.jpeg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/98/FM_Forbidden_Gundam.jpeg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20230807133634\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X252_Forbidden_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X252 Forbidden Gundam\">GAT-X252 Forbidden Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,800\n</td>\n<td>2023 August\n</td>\n<td>Fully transformable kit.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1096\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>FM #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th>\n<th>Link\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/c7/FM_Freedom_Gundam_Ver.GCP.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20210428155945\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"FM Freedom Gundam Ver.GCP\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"164\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"FM Freedom Gundam Ver.GCP.jpg\" data-image-key=\"FM_Freedom_Gundam_Ver.GCP.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/c7/FM_Freedom_Gundam_Ver.GCP.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20210428155945\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/ZGMF-X10A_Freedom_Gundam\" title=\"ZGMF-X10A Freedom Gundam\">ZGMF-X10A Freedom Gundam</a> Ver.GCP\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>RMB\u00a5339 / \u00a54,000\n</td>\n<td>2021 July (China) / 2021 August\n</td>\n<td>Tmall.com, P-Bandai and The Gundam Base exclusive release. Includes support stands to replicate the Life-Sized Freedom Gundam statue in Shanghai.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/17/FM_Aile_Calamity_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20230613133121\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"FM Aile Calamity Gundam\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"157\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"FM Aile Calamity Gundam.jpg\" data-image-key=\"FM_Aile_Calamity_Gundam.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/17/FM_Aile_Calamity_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20230613133121\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X130_Aile_Calamity_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X130 Aile Calamity Gundam\">GAT-X130 Aile Calamity Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED_Eclipse\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Eclipse\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Eclipse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,000\n</td>\n<td>2022 April\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive parts and color variant of FM-001.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/2357\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base Limited <a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X131_Calamity_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X131 Calamity Gundam\">Calamity Gundam</a> [Clear Color]\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,000\n</td>\n<td>2024 February\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base exclusive clear color variant of FM-001.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/XVX-016_Gundam_Aerial\" title=\"XVX-016 Gundam Aerial\">XVX-016 Gundam Aerial (Permet Score Six)</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_the_Witch_from_Mercury\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam the Witch from Mercury\">Mobile Suit Gundam the Witch from Mercury</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a54,200\n</td>\n<td>2024 March\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai and HYPER PLAMO Fes. 2024 exclusive color variant of FM-003. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/2522\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/a/ad/P_Bandai_1-100_FM_Sword_Calamity_Gundam_Box_Art_2024.png/revision/latest?cb=20240520010559\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"P Bandai 1-100 FM Sword Calamity Gundam Box Art 2024\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"164\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"P Bandai 1-100 FM Sword Calamity Gundam Box Art 2024.png\" data-image-key=\"P_Bandai_1-100_FM_Sword_Calamity_Gundam_Box_Art_2024.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/a/ad/P_Bandai_1-100_FM_Sword_Calamity_Gundam_Box_Art_2024.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20240520010559\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X133_Sword_Calamity\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"GAT-X133 Sword Calamity\">GAT-X133 Sword Calamity Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED_MSV\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED MSV\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED MSV</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,500\n</td>\n<td>2024 May\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive parts and color variant of FM-001.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/2486\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td>Prize A <a href=\"/wiki/XVX-016_Gundam_Aerial\" title=\"XVX-016 Gundam Aerial\">XVX-016 Gundam Aerial</a> Solid Clear\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_the_Witch_from_Mercury\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam the Witch from Mercury\">Mobile Suit Gundam the Witch from Mercury</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td>2024 August\n</td>\n<td>Banpresto exclusive re-release of FM-003 with clear color armor parts, offered as a lottery prize.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td>Prize Last One <a href=\"/wiki/XVX-016_Gundam_Aerial\" title=\"XVX-016 Gundam Aerial\">XVX-016 Gundam Aerial</a> Solid Clear Another\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_the_Witch_from_Mercury\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam the Witch from Mercury\">Mobile Suit Gundam the Witch from Mercury</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td>2024 August\n</td>\n<td>Banpresto exclusive re-release of FM-003 with clear color armor parts, offered as a lottery prize. Clear color armor parts are complementary to that in FM XVX-016 Gundam Aerial Solid Clear.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>2<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-XX370_Boost_Raider_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-XX370 Boost Raider Gundam\">GAT-XX370 Boost Raider Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED_Eclipse\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Eclipse\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Eclipse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a56,200\n</td>\n<td>2024 December\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive parts and color variant of FM-002.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/2494\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div></div>\n<p>Yen price excluding 10% tax.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Notes_.26_Trivia\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes_&amp;_Trivia\">Notes &amp; Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FFull_Mechanics%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FFull_Mechanics%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Master_Grade\" title=\"Master Grade\">Master Grade</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Reborn-One_Hundred\" title=\"Reborn-One Hundred\">Reborn-One Hundred</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/1/100_IRON-BLOODED_ORPHANS\" tit